Package: McDisCoV
Type: Package
Title: Microbiome Differential Discovery via Compositional Modeling under Varying Support
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jiahao Wang, Ruitao Liu
Maintainer: Ruitao Liu <rxl761@case.edu>
Description: Implements a compositional multivariate logistic-normal model with varying support
    for differential discovery in microbiome data. Supports efficient parameter estimation
    via parallel computation using RcppParallel and Eigen.
